{
  "stem": "16163.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told him, I said, I couldn't understand that he couldn't do anything for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he should have tried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not that my grandmother would have been alive at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was old already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she didn't have to go through that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You have a son in the States, you could have tried in the worst way, in the early '30s already to get out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was, I believe, in St.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Louis a baker.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I don't know if he had his own bakery or he worked for somebody or whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all right, there was a depression and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there were Jewish organizations then already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He could have at least tried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he didn't",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I really found out, also, from my cousin, who I met here again, who is the son of my father's sister who came here in 1933-- no, in 1936, '36 yes, in 1936, '37, around that time.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was about 15 years old at [BACKROUND NOISE] the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, he came with the children transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then was in an orphanage here, I believe, in New York for a few weeks or something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then when it was known that there is an uncle and family in St.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Louis, they got in touch with him, and he went to St.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Louis and stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But what I found out that my uncle got paid for him from a Jewish organization to have a foster child.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were-- then my cousin also told me that he took in other children to get paid for it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I don't know the circumstances, how well off they were or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
